3. License Activation, Recheck, and Telemetry
---------------------------------------------

The Software validates your license key with Licensor's licensing service on
first activation and periodically thereafter. As part of this validation, the
Software transmits your license key and a non-personally-identifying machine
fingerprint (a hashed combination of hostname, network adapter address, and
operating system identifiers) to the licensing service. No audio, video,
transcript, or recording content is ever transmitted as part of license
validation or any other automatic Software process.

The Software is permitted to operate offline for a grace period after the most
recent successful license recheck. Licensor reserves the right to revoke a
license key at any time for material breach of this Agreement, which will cause
the Software to refuse to launch on the next online recheck.

